unittitle_ssm: New-York Historical Society collection of geographic images
abstract_ssm:
This collection, formerly know as the Geographic File, includes prints, photographs, and some
newspaper clippings of street views and buildings in the five
boroughs of New York City (Series I through V), arranged by location or by type
of structure. Series VI contains views of the United
States outside of New York City, and Series VII consists of views outside of the United States.
subject_ssm: Commercial buildings -- New York (State)  -- New York.
Historic buildings -- New York (State)  -- New York.
Public buildings -- New York (State)  -- New York.
Public spaces -- New York (State)  -- New York -- Photographs.
Street life -- New York (State)  -- New York.
